column1: The file `academic-recommendation-app/output/recommendations.csv` is an output file and it will be generated by the program when it runs. It will contain the course recommendations for each student. Initially
column2: this file does not exist or is empty until the program is run. Therefore
column3: there is no code to provide for this file. It will be created and written to by the `write_csv` function in the `csv_processor.py` file.
